      <title>墨西哥尸体可能失踪美国和澳大利亚冲浪者</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/dead-bodies-mexico-likely-are-missing-us-australian-surfers-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥下加利福尼亚州一名高级官员周六表示，在墨西哥下加利福尼亚州发现的三具尸体很可能是上周失踪的美国游客和两名澳大利亚游客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/dead-bodies-mexico-likely-are-missing-us-australian-surfers-2024-05-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 19:23:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南警方逮捕前政府办公室主任</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-police-arrest-former-head-government-office-amid-anti-graft-crackdown-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南公安部周六表示，在东南亚国家不断扩大反腐打击力度之际，越南警方以涉嫌滥用职权的罪名逮捕了前政府办公室主任梅进勇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-police-arrest-former-head-government-office-amid-anti-graft-crackdown-2024-05-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 11:59:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前任命者表示，如果特朗普获胜，台湾将得到特朗普的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-have-trumps-support-if-he-wins-ex-appointee-says-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普任命的一位前美国大使周六表示，他相信这位前总统如果重新入主白宫，将再次支持台湾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-have-trumps-support-if-he-wins-ex-appointee-says-2024-05-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 09:58:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚南苏拉威西省洪水造成14人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/floods-indonesias-south-sulawesi-kill-14-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国灾害管理机构周六表示，大雨引发的洪水和山体滑坡已造成南苏拉威西省 14 人死亡，另有 115 人被疏散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/floods-indonesias-south-sulawesi-kill-14-2024-05-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 03:50:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰与德国南极洲合作研究所签署谅解备忘录</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/new-zealand-signs-mou-with-german-institute-antarctica-cooperation-2024-05-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰周六表示，随着中国在南极洲的影响力不断增强，其南极机构与德国阿尔弗雷德韦格纳研究所签署了一份谅解备忘录，以促进两个极地科学机构之间的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/new-zealand-signs-mou-with-german-institute-antarctica-cooperation-2024-05-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 02:25:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚和美国游客失踪墨西哥发现尸体</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/three-bodies-found-area-where-australian-us-tourists-went-missing-sources-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地检察官办公室周五晚间在一份声明中表示，墨西哥当局在下加利福尼亚州找到了三具尸体，据报一名美国游客和两名澳大利亚游客失踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/three-bodies-found-area-where-australian-us-tourists-went-missing-sources-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世卫组织总干事敦促各国在最后期限前敲定流行病协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/who-chief-urges-countries-finalise-pandemic-accord-by-deadline-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着本月谈判截止日期的临近，世界卫生组织总干事周五敦促各国同意达成一项协议，以帮助抗击未来的流行病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/who-chief-urges-countries-finalise-pandemic-accord-by-deadline-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国重量级人物他信的女儿称银行独立是“障碍”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/daughter-thai-heavyweight-thaksin-calls-cbank-independence-an-obstacle-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国颇具影响力的前总理他信·西那瓦(Thaksin Shinawatra)的政治家女儿周五表示，央行的独立性是解决经济问题的“障碍”，这是围绕利率的持续争论的最新一击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/daughter-thai-heavyweight-thaksin-calls-cbank-independence-an-obstacle-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:38:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪政党让有争议的议员儿子参加民意调查，印度摔跤运动员感到不安</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-wrestlers-upset-modis-party-fields-controversial-lawmakers-son-polls-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度顶级奥林匹克摔跤手批评总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党派前联合会主席的儿子参加全国选举，尽管他的父亲被指控性骚扰女摔跤手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-wrestlers-upset-modis-party-fields-controversial-lawmakers-son-polls-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:19:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ruang火山喷发后印尼将永久重新安置10,000人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-permanently-relocate-10000-people-after-ruang-volcano-eruptions-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼一位部长周五表示，鲁昂火山连续爆发引发人们对未来居住在该岛的危险性的担忧，印尼政府将永久安置近 10,000 名居民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-permanently-relocate-10000-people-after-ruang-volcano-eruptions-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
